EMERGENCY RECOVERY
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

If Everything Breaks:

1. Close all Command Prompts
2. Kill any Python processes:
   taskkill /IM python.exe /F
3. Restart computer
4. Navigate to project folder
5. Run batch file: START_BUDGET_APP.bat
6. If still broken, re-download files from Claude


